Package: radiant.design
Type: Package
Title: Design Menu for Radiant: Business Analytics using R and Shiny
Version: 0.8.9
Date: 2017-12-23
Authors@R: person("Vincent", "Nijs", , "radiant@rady.ucsd.edu", c("aut", "cre"))
